      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, and buyers should have realistic expectations before purchasing. The exterior shows moderate wear including some dents, scratches, and paint fading consistent with regular use over the years. The interior is functional but shows signs of age, with worn upholstery and minor scuffs on the trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This is a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind putting in a little work, and it is priced fairly to reflect its current state.",
