    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a practical ride that gets you where you need to go without a luxury price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, and with some care and attention, it has plenty of life left in it! Cosmetically, it shows its age with some wear inside and out, and there may be a few minor mechanical items worth addressing down the road. But for the budget-conscious buyer who wants reliable transportation today, this is a solid opportunity at an honest price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 16500.0,
