    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget ride or a project car? This vehicle is priced to move and represents an honest value for the right buyer! We won't sugarcoat it \u2014 this car shows significant wear inside and out, with mechanical issues that will need attention. It's best suited for a handy buyer, a project enthusiast, or someone in need of basic point-A-to-point-B transportation on a very tight budget. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just honest value!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition at $46,000, and that description is completely accurate and well-earned. The exterior is exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, rich, and glossy with no visible fading, chips, or scratches, looking as close to showroom-fresh as you'll find in the used market. The interior is equally impressive: all surfaces, upholstery, and trim are in pristine shape with no stains, tears, or worn areas whatsoever. Mechanically, this car is in top form \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function perfectly, and there are no warning lights or known issues. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that has been exceptionally well-maintained and truly shows it. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged \u2014 we are confident it will confirm everything described here.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Dependable & Honest \u2014 A Practical Ride at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude99 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's a solid everyday driver that gets you where you need to go! The exterior shows some visible wear and minor blemishes from regular use, giving it that lived-in look. Inside, the cabin is functional and comfortable, though you'll notice some signs of use here and there. Mechanically, it runs reliably for daily commutes and errands, though like any fair-condition vehicle, it may benefit from some attention down the road. If you're looking for an honest, no-surprises car at a budget-friendly price, this one's worth a look! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely flawless, with no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind; the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all trim pieces are pristine with no staining, cracking, fading, or wear. All mechanical systems are in excellent working order: the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly and quietly, and shows no leaks or unusual noises. Transmission shifts crisply and cleanly through all gears. Brakes are responsive and even. All electronics, lights, climate control, and infotainment features function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic fixes, no surprises. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed and will only confirm what is described here.",
      "price": 47500.0,
